data.description: Finally, the home you have been waiting for is now available and it has a NEW ROOF! From the moment you walk through the front door you will be in awe of the expansive, long lake views from just about every window.  Imagine waking up and enjoying the sunrise over the glistening lake. Or coming home after a long day and relaxing in the private pool while your pets play in the fenced backyard. This sprawling home boasts 4 BR plus a den and 3 full bathrooms. The split floor plan offers plenty of privacy from the grand, master suite featuring dual sinks, separate shower and a jetted tub. Your inner chef will delight in the enormous kitchen abounding with counter space and BRAND NEW APPLIANCES. Additional updates include newer A/C, pool equipment and exterior paint.  Located in a North Naples, gated community with low HOA fees that include cable & internet! Surrounded by 150 acres of freshwater lakes, community pool, tennis, pickle ball, basketball, volleyball and much more.  Close to "A" rated schools, shopping, restaurants and a public golf course.  Buy this home with peace of mind as it comes with a One Year Home Warranty.  Call today and make this house your home.
